        public Problem(java.lang.String title,
               java.lang.String description)

        Generates new problem object with given parameters. Comments is initialized as an empty list.

        title - Problem title (<=30 chars)
        description - Problem description (<= 300 chars)
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - thrown if title or description are of invalid length

      • deleteComment

        public java.lang.Boolean deleteComment(java.lang.String comment)
        Deletes comment matching the input string. Returns true on successful deletion, false if comment was not found in list.
        Parameters:

        Returns:
        true if comment was found and deleted, false otherwise

      • getRecords

      • addRecord

        public void addRecord(Record record)
        Add the given record to this problems record list. A record should not be associated with multiple problems.
        Parameters:
        record - Record object to be added.

      • removeRecord

        Parameters:

        Returns:
        True on successful deletion, False if the record was not found

      • getPhotos

        public java.util.ArrayList<Photo> getPhotos()
        Fetches a list comprised of all photos associated with all records associated with problem. Fetches photos from each record by method call every time this method is called, does not keep running list in Problem object.
        Returns:
        ArrayList of all photos of all associated records.
